    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>The Secret of Family Unity</strong>&mdash;The cause of division and discord in families and in the church is separation from Christ. To come near to Christ is to come near to one another. The secret of true unity in the church and in the family is not diplomacy, not management, not a superhuman effort to overcome difficulties&mdash;though there will be much of this to do&mdash;but union with Christ.",
